                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17440510-17-victim250 t17440510-17-viclabel93"></join>. The Prisoner has often robbed me of nails and iron; the last I know of, is, half an hundred of old coach streak nails; he took them away tub and all; but I could not light of him till last night.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17440510-17-person252">
                  Richard 
                  Lindup 
               <interp inst="t17440510-17-person252" type="surname" value="Lindup"></interp>
